They throw a first-mover into the camera. Seasoned sitters tell the guest:
- Well, choose what, either a fork in the eye or in the ass once.
The first step is breaking out of the hut. The turntable opens the door and asks:
- What are you trying to do, what do you need?
He answers:
- Why did you put me in a hut with a pid@ram?
The guests tensed up:
- What are you doing, confused? What kind of fags are we to you?
The first step says, explaining:
- And I don't see a single one-eyed one among you!
